 based on the premium between perpetual and spot prices. The funding rate is paid between long and short position holders, with a typical range of -0.375% to +0.375% per funding interval. Bitget's funding calculation uses a time-weighted average premium over the 8-hour period, smoothing out short-term volatility. Position holders must maintain their positions through the funding timestamp to pay or receive funding fees."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
